PrecisAppointment of MAX C. LEWIS of McLeod Hill, New Brunswick, to be Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 21, 2005, in the place of Emmanuel Triassi.
